This program is based on java, to run it, make sure your machine have java.

How to compile it: For server, type "javac Simple_ftp_server.java"
		 : For client, type "javac Simple_ftp_client"

How to run it: For server, type "java Simple_ftp_server port# file-name p"
	       For client, type "java Simple_ftp_client server-host-name server-port# file-name N MSS"
